made the ultimate sacrifice,

00:39.113 --> 00:44.618
113 local boys are unaccounted
for in the Pacific theater.

00:44.652 --> 00:47.554
They include Private
James Daryl of Bloomfield.

00:47.589 --> 00:50.490
Private Stuart Danforth of Bloomfield.

00:50.524 --> 00:54.195
Lance Corporal Francis R. Peabody.

00:54.229 --> 00:56.196
Private Hugo Bunker.

00:56.230 --> 00:59.933
Corporal George Higgins.
Private First Class...

01:38.973 --> 01:41.241
Son of a bitch.

02:04.365 --> 02:06.400
That's got to be north.

02:06.434 --> 02:07.801
Right?

02:11.005 --> 02:13.674
They said it would be just like Cambridge.

02:13.708 --> 02:14.841
Harvard with sand.

02:14.876 --> 02:17.310
Daddy's offer still stands.

02:17.344 --> 02:20.047
- It's a good job, Charles.
- It's a sales job.

02:20.081 --> 02:21.615
God forbid.

02:21.650 --> 02:23.784
You'd think a PhD was a vow of poverty.

02:23.818 --> 02:25.252
You know, business is a science.

02:25.286 --> 02:28.489
The recruiter said I could
be the next Enrico Fermi.

02:30.358 --> 02:33.427
He's like the Betty Grable of physics.

02:33.461 --> 02:35.062
Well, no one ever heard of him.

02:35.096 --> 02:37.865
Think of anyone heard of Galileo in 1590?

02:37.899 --> 02:41.702
I bet Galileo knew how to read a road map.

02:50.111 --> 02:52.613
Yeah, that's north.

02:52.647 --> 02:55.549
Joey, come on.

